'''INBRIDING''' (inl. Inbreeding- yakyn garyndashlara kopelish) – yakyn garyndashlara mallary gatyshdyryp tohumlandyrmak arkaly kopeltmek, atanaklayyn tozalanyan osumlikleri mejbury suratda oz ozunden tozanlandyryp kopeltmek. Tebigy Inbriding osumlikcilikde maldarcylykdaka garanda adaty hadysadyr. Bugday, arpa, shaly nohut, noyba, arahos, soya, pomidor, burc, shetdaly we gowaca yaly birentek ekinler oz ozunden tozanlanyar. Inbriding uzak wagtlap dowam etse, osumliklerde we mallarda zyyanly resessiw genlerin tasirinin yuze cykmagy mumkin, bu bolsa kemciligin doremegine, onumliligin yashaysh ukyplylygynyn peselmegine eltip biler. Mallarda (seyrek halatda osumliklerde-de) Inbriding gecirilende yashayysh ukyplylygy kadaly bolan ayry ugurlary almak bolyar.

